checks.name: Alt-Text; Images;
checks.description:
Failure due to representing informative images as styled
elements instead of semantic image elements ( or role='img'), making them inaccessible to assistive technologies.

issues.title: Elements must meet minimum color contrast ratio thresholds
issues.description: Ensure the contrast between foreground and background colors meets WCAG 2 AA minimum contrast ratio thresholds
